n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>VERSION 1.0.2 &#8211; Released: Dec 29, 2014</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Yit_Plugin_Panel_WooCommerce class do not exists.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>VERSION 1.0.1 &#8211; Released: Dec 23, 20141.0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated: Plugin core framework</li>\n<li>Tweak: Plugin options page</li>\n<li>Fixed: Minor bugs</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:3873:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1606388\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1606388\" alt=\"This is the general setting page, you can find it in &quot;YIT Plugins&quot; menu item. There you can set if a title should be shown on review submit form and on review content. You can also set if enable attachments and how many files the client is allowed to append.\"></a><p>This is the general setting page, you can find it in \"YIT Plugins\" menu item. There you can set if a title should be shown on review submit form and on review content. You can also set if enable attachments and how many files the client is allowed to append.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1606388\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1606388\" alt=\"Convert all previously created reviews to YITH WooCommerce Advanced Reviews format, without losing any data.\"></a><p>Convert all previously created reviews to YITH WooCommerce Advanced Reviews format, without losing any data.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1606388\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1606388\" alt=\"Customize the summary bar background, foreground and text color and if the percentage value must be shown inside the percentage bars.\"></a><p>Customize the summary bar b