ble, in colour, text and position. Yet, a suggestion: do not exaggerate! A different badge for each product is like putting none upon them.</p>\n<h4>Features:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>A specific panel to create unlimited textual badges. Options allow to set badge colour, text, text colour and badge position.</li>\n<li>5 image badges included in the plugin, with a graphic by YIThemes.</li>\n<li>A select menu for each product to choose the type of badge to set.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Suggestions</h3>\n<p>If you have suggestions about how to improve YITH WooCommerce Badge Management, you can <a href=\"mailto:&#112;&#108;&#x75;&#x67;&#x69;&#x6e;&#x73;&#064;&#121;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#x65;&#x6d;&#x65;&#x73;&#x2e;&#099;&#111;&#109;\" title=\"Your Inspiration Themes\" rel=\"nofollow\">write us</a> so we can bundle them into YITH WooCommerce Badge Management.</p>\n<h3>Translators</h3>\n<h4>Available Languages</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>English (Default)</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:440:\"<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Badge Management</code> from Plugins page</li>\n</ol>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Badge Management will add a new submenu called &#8220;Badge Management&#8221; under &#8220;YIT Plugins&#8221; menu. Here you are able to configure all the plugin settings.</p>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:5246:\"<h4>1.3.4 &#8211; Released: May 09, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; badge saving</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; hidden badges in feeds</li>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; removed badges in wishlist table of YITH WooCommerce Wishlist</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.3 &#8211; Released: Apr 11, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WooCommerce 3.0.1</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; post thumbnail issue</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.2 &#8211; Released: Apr 05, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WooCommerce 3.0.0</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; badge saving</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.1 &#8211; Released: Mar 31, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WooCommerce 3.0.0-RC2</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; removed inline badge styles</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.0 &#8211; Released: Mar 10, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WooCommerce 2.7.0-RC1</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WordPress 4.7.3</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.13 &#8211; Released: Jan 27, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; badge style issue</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.12 &#8211; Released: Dec 23, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; duplicate badges</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; removed badge permalink</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.11 &#8211; Released: Oct 26, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; added missing files</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; hidden badges in Storefront Sticky Add to Cart</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.10 &#8211; Released: Sep 23, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WordPress 4.6.1</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; badges in YITH WooCommerce Recently Viewed Products emails hidden because causing graphical issues</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; badges in YITH WooCommerce Questions and Answers emails hidden because causing graphical issues</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; issues in combination with Storefront Sticky Add to Cart</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; badge styles W3C</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.9 &#8211; Released: Jul 08, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WordPress 4.5.3</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WooCommerce 2.6.2</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to ajax loading of product thumbnails</li>\n<li>New &#8211; Italian language</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.8 &#8211; Released: Apr 29, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WordPress 4.5.1</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WooCommerce 2.5.5</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to Flatsome</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to YITH WooCommerce Wishlist</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to YITH WooCommerce Frequently Bought Together</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to YITH WooCommerce Save for Later</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to YITH WooCoomerce Ajax Search</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to YITH WooCommerce Product Bundles</li>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; prevent badges from showing in WooCommerce emails</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.7 &#8211; Released: Jan 22, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WordPress 4.4.1</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WooCommerce 2.5</li>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; hidden badges in WooCommerce mini-cart</li>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; fixed minor bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.6 &#8211; Released: Dec 21, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; fixed minor bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.5 &#8211; Released: Dec 18, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WordPress 4.4</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WooCommerce 2.4.12</li>\n<li>New &#8211; possibility to show/hide badges in sidebars</li>\n<li>New &#8211; possibility to show/hide WooCommerce default &#8220;On Sale&#8221; badge when the product has another badge.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.3 &#8211; Released: Dec 01, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; fixed minor bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.2 &#8211; Released: Nov 09, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Compatibility with more themes</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.1 &#8211; Released: Oct 28, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; minor bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.9 &#8211; Released: Aug 21, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WordPress 4.3</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; removed badges in cart and checkout</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; minor bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.7 &#8211; Released: Aug 14, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WooCommerce 2.4.4</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.6 &#8211; Released: Aug 12, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WordPress 4.2.4</li>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WooCommerce 2.4.2</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; WPML deprecated functions</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.5 &#8211; Released: Jul 24, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; WPML Compatibility</li>\n<li>New &#8211; Compatibility with more themes</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Bug with widget sidebar on header</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.4 &#8211; Released: Jul 10, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WooCommerce shortcodes</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Compatibility with more themes</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.3 &#8211; Released: Jul 03, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; badge display in widget top related product</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.2 &#8211; Released: Jun 19, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Wrong admin css handle</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.1 &#8211; Released: May 29, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WooCommce 2.3.9</li>\n<li>Update &#8211; Default language file</li>\n<li>Update &#8211; Plugin framework</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Can&#8217;t make a badge issue</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.0 &#8211; Released: May 08, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WordPress 4.2.2</li>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WooCommerce 2.3.8</li>\n<li>Update &#8211; Default language file</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Duplicate product image in shop loop</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Minor bugs</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.0 &#8211; Released: Mar 25, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:486:\"\n<h4>Installation Instructions</h4>\n<p>\n<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Badge Management</code> from Plugins page</li>\n</ol>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Badge Management will add a new submenu called &#8220;Badge Management&#8221; under &#8220;YIT Plugins&#8221; menu. Here you are able to configure all the plugin settings.</p>\n</p>\n\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:2571:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-badges-management/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1611885\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-badges-management/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1611885\" alt=\"Admin: Badges list\"></a><p>Admin: Badges list</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-badges-management/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1611885\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-badges-management/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1611885\" alt=\"Admin: Add new custom badge\"></a><p>Admin: Add new custom badge</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocom