n <a href=\"mailto:&#112;&#108;&#x75;&#x67;&#x69;&#x6e;&#x73;&#064;&#121;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#x65;&#x6d;&#x65;&#x73;&#x2e;&#099;&#111;&#109;\" title=\"Your Inspiration Themes\" rel=\"nofollow\">write us</a> so we can bundle them into YITH Live Chat.</p>\n<h3>Translators</h3>\n<h4>Available Languages</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>English</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you have created your own language pack, or have an update for an existing one, you can send <a href=\"https://codex.wordpress.org/Translating_WordPress\" title=\"Translating WordPress\" rel=\"nofollow\">gettext PO and MO file</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://yithemes.com/contact/\" title=\"Your Inspiration Themes\" rel=\"nofollow\">use</a> so we can bundle it into YITH Live Chat languages.</p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:519:\"<h4>Installation</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH Live Chat</code> from Plugins page.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Configuration</h4>\n<p>YITH Live Chat will add a new tab called &#8220;Live Chat&#8221; inside the YIT Plugins menu, where you will be able to configure all plugin settings, and a new menu item called &#8220;YITH Live Chat&#8221;, where there is the chat console.</p>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:2408:\"<h4>Version 1.2.2 &#8211; Released: Nov 7, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: added missing files</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.1 &#8211; Released: Oct 12, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: support for CJK characters</li>\n<li>Fixed: end conversation issue</li>\n<li>Tweak: Optimized Frontend and Console templates</li>\n<li>Tweak: optimized JS and CSS loading</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.5 &#8211; Released: Apr 20, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: minified version of CSS files</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.4 &#8211; Released: Mar 02, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: hidden on the console page, notifications that disturb the positioning</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.3 &#8211; Released: Feb 09, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: show offline message if Firebase loses connection</li>\n<li>Fixed: chat page lost during page switch</li>\n<li>Fixed: notification counter showing incorrect values</li>\n<li>Fixed: minor bugs</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.2 &#8211; Released: Oct 30, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated: changed text domain from ylc to yith-live-chat</li>\n<li>Updated: changed all language file for the new text domain</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.1 &#8211; Released: Oct 29, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated: plugin core framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.0 &#8211; Released: Oct 15, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: Frontend login username now accepts characters from these Unicode sets: Greek and Coptic, Arabian, Cyrillic, Armenian, Hebrew and Latin-1 (only chars with grave, acute, diaeresis, circumflex, etc.)</li>\n<li>Added: minified version of all JS files</li>\n<li>Tweak: Changed global $yith_livechat object to YITH_Live_Chat() singleton.</li>\n<li>Fixed: separated JS files for frontend and console</li>\n<li>Various code improvements</li>\n<li>Updated language file</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.5 &#8211; Released: Aug 15, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: Support to WooCommerce 2.4</li>\n<li>Updated: Plugin core framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.4 &#8211; Released: July 31, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: session destroy bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.3 &#8211; Released: July 09, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: session destroy bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.2 &#8211; Released: May 18, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Code Improvements</li>\n<li>Updated language file</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.1 &#8211; Released: May 15, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Code Improvements</li>\n<li>Update core plugin</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.0 &#8211; Released: Mar 27, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:1595:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-live-chat/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1625660\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-live-chat/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=16