h-live-chat.1.2.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.2\";s:63:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-live-chat.1.2.2.zip\";s:5:\"trunk\";s:57:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-live-chat.zip\";}s:11:\"donate_link\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"icons\";a:1:{s:2:\"1x\";s:67:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-live-chat/assets/icon-128x128.jpg?rev=1466779\";}s:12:\"contributors\";a:0:{}}}s:23:\"yith-woocommerce-eu-vat\";a:5:{s:4:\"name\";s:23:\"YITH WooCommerce EU VAT\";s:4:\"slug\";s:23:\"yith-woocommerce-eu-vat\";s:15:\"premium_constat\";s:17:\"YITH_YWEV_PREMIUM\";s:4:\"file\";s:8:\"init.php\";s:7:\"wp_info\";a:26:{s:4:\"name\";s:23:\"YITH WooCommerce EU VAT\";s:4:\"slug\";s:23:\"yith-woocommerce-eu-vat\";s:7:\"version\";s:6:\"1.2.10\";s:6:\"author\";s:43:\"<a href=\"http://yithemes.com/\">YITHEMES</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:39:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yithemes\";s:8:\"requires\";s:5:\"3.5.1\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"4.7.5\";s:6:\"rating\";i:0;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:0;i:4;i:0;i:3;i:0;i:2;i:0;i:1;i:0;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:0;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:0;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:0;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:100;s:10:\"downloaded\";i:3490;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:21:\"2017-04-30 9:39am GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2015-04-09\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:59:\"http://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-eu-vat/\";s:8:\"sections\";a:5:{s:11:\"description\";s:2355:\"<p>From January 1st 2015, the European Union has put into effect the new rules about the taxation on the purchase of all digital goods for European citizens.<br />\nThis makes necessary to apply the right taxes for every purchaser of your e-commerce.<br />\nTherefore, whether your users are direct consumers or businesses, YITH WooCommerce EU VAT allows your customers to be identified by their country, applying automatically the expected taxes, and summarizing all the amounts you will have to pay monthly. An efficient and automatic tool to respect the new legislation.</p>\n<h4>Main features</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Taxes are applied based on the customer location.</li>\n<li>Pre built EU Tax rates list.</li>\n<li>Choose the taxes to pay with a MOSS report filtered by nation and time</li>\n<li>Choose to prevent purchases from EU customers.</li>\n<li>In case of you want to prevent purchases from EU customers, choose to show customized messages on cart and on checkout page.</li>\n<li>Store automatically the EU taxes paid by the customer.</li>\n<li>Consult quickly a direct report about the taxes to pay by nation and period of time.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>For a more detailed list of options and features of the plugin, please look at the <a href=\"http://yithemes.com/docs-plugins/yith-woocommerce-eu-vat/\" title=\"Yith WooCommerce EU VAT official documentation\" rel=\"nofollow\">official documentation</a>.</p>\n<p>Discover all the features of the plugin and install it in your theme: the result will be extremely satisfying.</p>\n<h3>Suggestions</h3>\n<p>If you have any suggestions concerning how to improve YITH WooCommerce EU VAT, you can <a href=\"mailto:&#112;&#108;&#x75;&#x67;&#x69;&#x6e;&#x73;&#064;&#121;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#x65;&#x6d;&#x65;&#x73;&#x2e;&#099;&#111;&#109;\" title=\"Your Inspiration Themes\" rel=\"nofollow\">write to us</a>, so that we can improve YITH WooCommerce EU VAT.</p>\n<h3>Translators</h3>\n<h4>Available Languages</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>English</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you have created your own language pack, or you have got an updated version of an existing one, you can send it <a href=\"https://codex.wordpress.org/Translating_WordPress\" title=\"Translating WordPress\" rel=\"nofollow\">gettext PO and MO file</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://yithemes.com/contact/\" title=\"Your Inspiration Themes\" rel=\"nofollow\">use</a>, so that we can improve YITH WooCommerce EU VAT.</p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:631:\"<p>Important: First of all, you have to download and activate WooCommerce plugin, which is mandatory for YITH WooCommerce EU VAT to be working.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Download and unzip the downloaded file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce EU VAT</code> from &#8220;Plugins&#8221; page.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Configuration</h4>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce EU VAT will add a new tab called &#8220;EU VAT&#8221; in &#8220;YIT Plugins&#8221; menu item. There, you will find all Yithemes plugins with quick access to plugin setting page.</p>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:2144:\"<h4>Version 1.2.10 &#8211; Released: Apr 30, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: YITH Plugin Framework.</li>\n<li>Tweak: tested up to WordPress 4.7.4.</li>\n<li>Tweak: changed plugin tags.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.9 &#8211; Released: Mar 24, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New:  Support to WooCommerce 3.0.0-RC1</li>\n<li>Update: YITH Plugin Framework</li>\n<li>Fix: YITH Plugin Framework initialization.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.8 &#8211; Released: Jan 16, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: WordPress 4.7 ready</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.7 &#8211; Released: Jun 13, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated: WooCommerce 2.6 100% compatible</li>\n<li>Fixed: removed deprecated action woocommerce_update_option_x</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.6 &#8211; Released: May 04, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: missing YITH Plugin FW files</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.5 &#8211; Released: May 02, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated: plugin compatible with WordPress 4.5</li>\n<li>Updated: plugin author name </li>\n<li>Updated: YITH Plugin Framework</li>\n<li>Fixed: some string were not localizable</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.4 &#8211; Released: Nov 23, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated: changed action used for YITH Plugin FW loading from after_setup_theme to plugins_loaded</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.3 &#8211; Released: Oct 29, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: update YITH Plugin framework.</li>\n<li>Update: changed text-domain from ywev to yith-woocommerce-eu-vat</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.2 &#8211; Released: Aug 12, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: update YITH Plugin framework.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.1 &#8211; Released: Jul 03, 2015</h4>\n<p>=</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix : misspelling on constant name</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.0 &#8211; Released: May 21, 2015</h4>\n<p>=</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix : support WooCommerce plugin version prior than 2.3.0</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.0 &#8211; Released: Apr 22, 2015</h4>\n<p>=</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix : security issue (https://make.wordpress.org/plugins/2015/04/20/fixing-add_query_arg-and-remove_query_arg-usage/)</li>\n<li>Tweak : support up to WordPress 4.2</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.1 &#8211; Released: Apr 16, 2015</h4>\n<p>=</p>\n<p>Added : videobox information.</p>\n<h4>1.0.0</h4>\n<p>Initial release</p>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:677:\"\n<h4>Installation Instructions</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Important: First of all, you have to download and activate WooCommerce plugin, which is mandatory for YITH WooCommerce EU VAT to be working.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Download and unzip the downloaded file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce EU VAT</code> from &#8220;Plugins&#8221; page.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Configuration</h4>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce EU VAT will add a new tab called &#8220;EU VAT&#8221; in &#8220;YIT Plugins&#8221; menu item. There, you will find all Yithemes plugins with quick access to plugin setting page.</p>\n</p>\n\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:3371:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-eu-vat/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1586422\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-eu-vat/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1586422\" alt=\"In order to deal with EU VAT laws, the shop owner can decide to deny purchases from EU customers.\"></a><p>In order to deal with EU VAT laws, the shop owner can decide to deny purchases from EU customers.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-eu-vat/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1586422\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-eu-vat/assets/scre