infinite-scrolling\";a:5:{s:4:\"name\";s:23:\"YITH Infinite Scrolling\";s:4:\"slug\";s:23:\"yith-infinite-scrolling\";s:15:\"premium_constat\";s:17:\"YITH_INFS_PREMIUM\";s:4:\"file\";s:8:\"init.php\";s:7:\"wp_info\";a:26:{s:4:\"name\";s:23:\"YITH Infinite Scrolling\";s:4:\"slug\";s:23:\"yith-infinite-scrolling\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.0.7\";s:6:\"author\";s:44:\"<a href=\"https://yithemes.com/\">YITHEMES</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:39:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yithemes\";s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"4.0\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"4.7.5\";s:6:\"rating\";d:98;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:16;i:4;i:1;i:3;i:0;i:2;i:0;i:1;i:0;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:17;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:6;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:1;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:8000;s:10:\"downloaded\";i:61911;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:21:\"2016-12-19 4:50pm GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2015-03-12\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:60:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-infinite-scrolling/\";s:8:\"sections\";a:5:{s:11:\"description\";s:1920:\"<p><strong>They want it all right away!</strong></p>\n<p>People have become used to see contents online in a sequential way: think about Facebook or Twitter, two navigation systems that now influence how we browse the web. With <strong>YITH Infinite Scrolling</strong>, we have decided to apply this idea for an <strong>immediate and direct consultation</strong> of the page contents!</p>\n<p>No more loading times caused by the change of the page, well, no more pages for a unique category of elements! Everything will come in a single solution, where users, even from a mobile device, will be able to simply scroll down and <strong>get the details they seek right away</strong>, without being afraid to lose them loading a new page.</p>\n<p><strong>Main features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>The infinite scrolling offers an amount of products all showed at once</li>\n<li>Simple and direct navigation, even from a mobile device</li>\n<li>Transition effect</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Full documentation is available <a href=\"http://yithemes.com/docs-plugins/yith-infinite-scrolling/\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>.</p>\n<h3>Suggestions</h3>\n<p>If you have suggestions about how to improve YITH Infinite Scrolling, you can <a href=\"mailto:&#112;&#108;&#x75;&#x67;&#x69;&#x6e;&#x73;&#064;&#121;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#x65;&#x6d;&#x65;&#x73;&#x2e;&#099;&#111;&#109;\" title=\"Your Inspiration Themes\" rel=\"nofollow\">write us</a> so we can bundle them into YITH Infinite Scrolling.</p>\n<h3>Translators</h3>\n<h4>Available Languages</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>English</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you have created your own language pack, or have an update for an existing one, you can send <a href=\"https://codex.wordpress.org/Translating_WordPress\" title=\"Translating WordPress\" rel=\"nofollow\">gettext PO and MO file</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://yithemes.com/contact/\" title=\"Your Inspiration Themes\" rel=\"nofollow\">use</a> so we can bundle it into YITH Infinite Scrolling languages.</p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:235:\"<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH Infinite Scrolling</code> from Plugins page.</li>\n</ol>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:169:\"<ul>\n<li>It&#8217;s compatible with WooCommerce?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Yes, of course. This plugin is fully compatible with WooCommerce 2.6 and previous versions until 2.2.</p>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:1072:\"<h4>1.0.7</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: Support to WordPress 4.7.</li>\n<li>Added: Support to WooCommerce 2.6.9.</li>\n<li>Updated: Plugin Core.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.6</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: Compatibility with WordPress 4.5</li>\n<li>Added: Added minimized js files. Plugin loads full files version if the constant &#8220;SCRIPT_DEBUG&#8221; is defined and is true.</li>\n<li>Updated: Plugin Core</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.5</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated: Language file. Changed text domain from yith-infs to yith-infinite-scrolling</li>\n<li>Updated: Plugin Core</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: Compatibility with YITH WooCommerce Ajax Product Filter</li>\n<li>Added: Compatibility with YITH WooCommerce Color Label Variations</li>\n<li>Updated: Plugin Core</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: Compatibility with WooCommerce 2.4</li>\n<li>Updated: Plugin Core</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed plugin documentation link</li>\n<li>Fixed plugin core</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Minor bugfix</li>\n<li>Fixed plugin core</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:255:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-infinite-scrolling/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1625798\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-infinite-scrolling/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1625798\" alt=\"The plugin admin page.\"></a><p>The plugin admin page.</p></li></ol>\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:52:\"Add infinite scrolling to archive post or shop page.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:72:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-infinite-scrolling.1.0.7.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:1:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:76:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-infinite-scrolling/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1625798\";s:7:\"caption\";s:22:\"The plugin admin page.\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:5:{s:18:\"infinite-scrolling\";s:18:\"infinite scrolling\";s:11:\"woocommerce\";s:11:\"woocommerce\";s:30:\"woocommerce-infinite-scrolling\";s:30:\"woocommerce infinite scrolling\";s:3:\"yit\";s:3:\"yit\";s:4:\"yith\";s:4:\"yith\";}s:8:\"versions\";a:9:{s:5:\"1.0.0\";s:72:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-infinite-scrolling.1.0.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.1\";s:72:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-infinite-scrolling.1.0.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.2\";s:72:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-infinite-scrolling.1.0.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.3\";s:72:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-infinite-scrolling.1.0.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.4\";s:72:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-infinite-scrolling.1.0.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.5\";s:72:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-infinite-scrolling.1.0.5.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.6\";s:72:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-infinite-scrolling.1.0.6.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.7\";s:72:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-infinite-scrolling.1.0.7.zip\";s:5:\"trunk\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-infinite-scrolling.zip\";}s:11:\"donate_link\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"icons\";a:1:{s:2:\"1x\";s:76:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-infinite-scrolling/assets/icon-128x128.jpg?rev=1111021\";}s:12:\"contributors\";a:0:{}}}s:29:\"yith-woocommerce-waiting-list\";a:5:{s:4:\"name\";s:29:\"YITH WooCommerce Waiting List\";s:4:\"slug\";s:29:\"yith-woocommerce-waiting-list\";s:15:\"premium_constat\";s:18:\"YITH_WCWTL_PREMIUM\";s:4:\"file\";s:8:\"init.php\";s:7:\"wp_info\";a:26:{s:4:\"name\";s:29:\"YITH WooCommerce Waiting List\";s:4:\"slug\";s:29:\"yith-woocommerce-waiting-list\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.1.1\";s:6:\"author\";s:44:\"<a href=\"https://yithemes.com/\">YITHEMES</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:39:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yithemes\";s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"4.0\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"4.7.5\";s:6:\"rating\";d:58;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:7;i:4;i:0;i:3;i:1;i:2;i:0;i:1;i:8;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:16;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:1;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:1;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:1000;s:10:\"downloaded\";i:11496;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:21:\"2017-04-21 1:40pm GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2015-04-07\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:65:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list\";s:8:\"sections\";a:5:{s:11:\"description\";s:1758:\"<p>What do you do when you have no more stock of one of your products and your customers want to buy it? You risk to lose them, unless you make a system available for them to be notified of the product coming back to stock. Then, why not using a plugin that allows them to be added to a waiting list and being informed in an automatic and efficient way? This is what YITH WooCommerce Waiting List does, allowing you to loyalise them in a simple way and at the same time not lose them.</p>\n<p><strong>Main features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>A form to receive a reminding email when the item is back in stock</li>\n<li>&#8220;Add me to the waiting list&#8221; button for logged users</li>\n<li>Summary metabox with the number of waiting user and a rapid way to contact them</li>\n<li>Customization of the &#8220;Notify me&#8221; button</li>\n<li>Email basic template to notify users for an item back in stock</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Suggestions</h3>\n<p>If you have suggestions about how to improve YITH WooCommerce Waiting List, you can <a href=\"mailto:&#112;&#108;&#x75;&#x67;&#x69;&#x6e;&#x73;&#064;&#121;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#x65;&#x6d;&#x65;&#x73;&#x2e;&#099;&#111;&#109;\" title=\"Your Inspiration Themes\" rel=\"nofollow\">write us</a> so we can bundle them into YITH WooCommerce Waiting List.</p>\n<h3>Translators</h3>\n<h4>Available Languages</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>English</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you have created your own language pack, or have an update for an existing one, you can send <a href=\"https://codex.wordpress.org/Translating_WordPress\" title=\"Translating WordPress\" rel=\"nofollow\">gettext PO and MO file</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://yithemes.com/contact/\" title=\"Your Inspiration Themes\" rel=\"nofollow\">use</a> so we can bundle it into YITH WooCommerce Waiting List languages.</p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:241:\"<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Waiting List</code> from Plugins page.</li>\n</ol>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:448:\"<ul>\n<li>It&#8217;s compatible with WooCommerce?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Yes, of course. This plugin is full compatible with WooCommerce 2.3 and previous version 2.2.</p>\n\n<h4>Installation Instructions</h4>\n<p>\n<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Waiting List</code> from Plugins page.</li>\n</ol>\n</p>\n\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:2370:\"<h4>1.1.1</h4>\n<p>Released Apr 21 &#8211; 2017</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 3.0.4.</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n<li>Fix: Prevent duplicated post meta for product.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.0</h4>\n<p>Released Mar 29 &#8211; 2017</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 3.0.0 RC2.</li>\n<li>New: Support to WordPress 4.7.3.</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.8</h4>\n<p>Released Jan 13 &#8211; 2017</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Shortcode for print waiting list form [yith_wcwtl_form].</li>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 2.6.7.</li>\n<li>New: Support to WordPress 4.7.1.</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n<li>Dev: Add filter for form html &#8216;yith_wcwtl_form_html&#8217;.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.7</h4>\n<p>Released Nov 07 &#8211; 2016</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WordPress 4.6.1</li>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 2.6.7</li>\n<li>New: &#8220;In Stock Email Settings&#8221; panel on plugin options.</li>\n<li>New: Option for change email content directly from plugin panel.</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.6</h4>\n<p>Released May 24 &#8211; 2016</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WordPress 4.5.2.</li>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 2.6 Beta2.</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.5</h4>\n<p>Released Apr 15 &#8211; 2016</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WordPress 4.5.</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.4</h4>\n<p>Released Jan 07 &#8211; 2016</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 2.5 BETA.</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n<li>Update: Language file .pot.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.3</h4>\n<p>Released Nov 03 &#8211; 2015</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: xml config file for wpml.</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin core.</li>\n<li>Update: Language file. Changed text domain from yith-wcwtl to yith-woocommerce-waiting-list.</li>\n<li>Fix: Add users email in BBC ( thanks to jedelucca and Spartan_SA from wordpress support forum ).</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.2</h4>\n<p>Released Aug 13 &#8211; 2015</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 2.4.</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin core.</li>\n<li>Update: Language file.</li>\n<li>Fix: Plugin documentation link.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.1</h4>\n<p>Released Apr 22 &#8211; 2015</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WordPress 4.2.</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n<li>Fix: Form for variation product.</li>\n<li>Fix: Send mail for variation product.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.0</h4>\n<p>Released Mar 31 &#8211; 2015</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:823:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1625824\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1625824\" alt=\"The plugin admin page.\"></a><p>The plugin admin page.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1625824\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1625824\" alt=\"Plugin frontend for logged in user\"></a><p>Plugin frontend for logged in user</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=1625824\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=1625824\" alt=\"Plugin frontend for guest user\"></a><p>Plugin frontend for guest user</p></li></ol>\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:112:\"This plugin enables registered users to request an email notification when an out-of-stock product comes&hellip;\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list.1.1.1.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:3:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:82:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-waiting-list/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1625824\";s:7:\"caption\";s:22:\"The plugin admin page.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\